blog.description:
Hello! I’m Rose, 16 and I absolutely love Marvel very very much! Send me asks and what not so we can freal out and fan over Marvel together. 
THIS IS A SIDE BLOG, you can follow me at Fangirlxrose

body:
Marvel Talk (January 1st)

It’s the first Marvel Talk of 2019! This first one is about Marvel Female characters.

I was talking to 2 of my friends about Marvel and we were saying how we would absolutely love more awesome, badass and overall amazing female characters in the MCU. To me I think Captain Marvel will hopefully be a step into the right direction. I love so many of the other female characters too in the MCU but I just want to see more! I love the female characters in ‘Agents of Shield’ they are awesome to me and we need that to carry over to the MCU.

What do you all think?
